snippet.title: Tony Hawk's Pro Skater 2 [N64] - Intro & Gameplay Demo
snippet.description:
First of all. I suck at this game... hard.
Second: This is a raw video (means no editing) that was captured from both actual N64 System and THPS2 Cartridge, using an S-Video Cable.

The video features the following modes:
Career
Track Editor
Create Skater (Skater Editor)
Single Session
Free Skate
